<h2>1968/2008 - Revision einer kulturellen Formation (Sammelband)</h2>
<h3></h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='503'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h3>Allgemeine Angaben</h3>
